<h2 id="head-12e66e350586926a1dee42658553b0525f6f12ad">Module Ideas</h2>
<p>
This is a list of proposed module ideas. Feel free to add your own... 
</p>

    <ul>

    <li>
<p>
 <a href="./Modules_2fAge_20of_20Myth">/Age of Myth</a> : When the Earth was young and mankind was only one of it's races... 
</p>
</li>
    <li>
<p>
 <a href="./Modules_2fAnnals_20of_20the_20Riftwar">/Annals of the Riftwar</a> : Feistian 
</p>
</li>
    <li>
<p>
 <a href="./Modules_2fChill_20Out_20Mod">/Chill Out Mod</a> : Play after heavy ToME sessions 
</p>
</li>
    <li>
<p>
 <a href="./Modules_2fColdfire">/Coldfire</a> : Based on the books by C. S Friedman 
</p>
</li>
    <li>
<p>
 <a href="./Modules_2fDragon_20Ball">/Dragon Ball</a> : Based of the TV series Dragon Ball, DBZ and DBGT. 
</p>
</li>
    <li>
<p>
 <a href="./Modules_2fDrangBand">/DrangBand</a> : The Dragon Tower is in turmoil, it's faith is in your hands 
</p>
</li>
    <li>
<p>
 <a href="./Modules_2fGalactic_20Center">/Galactic Center</a> : Science fiction mod based on the books by Benford 
